## Current Priority Symptoms (2025)
1. **Respiratory control dysfunction** - loss of automatic breathing drive
2. **Progressive tremor patterns** - head, hands, vocal involvement
3. **Autonomic instability** - daily tachycardia, rigid awakening patterns
4. **Motor system freeze states** - new development post-May 29 episode

